description:
The trance flavoured 120 bpm 'Original Mix' features a huge break with arpeggiated chords and lush synth textures.

The 118 bpm 'Sunset Mix' is a downbeat reworking of the original, and pays tribute to the famous Sunset DJ and compiler at Caf√© del Mar Jose Padilla. 
{Listen here: https://li.sten.to/radiance-linktree}

Both artists have worked with him in Ibiza, he was a huge inspiration to many.

"Radiance is the radiant flux emitted, reflected, transmitted or received by a given surface."

As Science fiction fans there was always a fascination with vivid lights of the night sky. These artefacts, monoliths and the possibility of otherworldly places and intelligence in the unfathomable vastness of space inspired 'Radiance'...

This release renews an old partnership collaborating closely with the producer Gena Wernik.

The 121 bpm track is divided in 3 sections: 
Meditation - Extasy - Arrival

description:
Millions of listeners all over the world enjoy the mesmerising music of the Persian artist Bahramji, who calls Ibiza home.
Long before Berlin based producer Chris Zippel moved to the island and became friends with the musician, Bahram's Chill Out Albums ‚ÄúSufi Safir‚Äù and ‚ÄúSufiyan‚Äù in collaboration with the artist Mashti had a huge impact on him. 
Their co-creation on the track SANDS features Bahrams unique way of singing and playing his trademark 72-string instrument, the Santur;

Combined with the productions skills of veteran producer Chris the track comes in a tempo of 113 Bpm in different mixes and dub versions.

May all beings be happy and at peace!

description:
This is the final chapter of the Petrichor / Hiraeth series "REMIXED" featuring artists like Riccicomoto, Aiora, STR3E & Chris Zippel.


Riccicomoto 
is an Ibiza based producer with his own radio show on Ibiza Global Radio. He is known for his atmospheric dub techno and cineastic
sound, preparing an album release on his own now on Big Al¬¥s ‚ÄúReady Mix Records‚Äù this summer.

STR3E
The classically trained Sa√Ød Daghelfi aka STR3E  (pronounced S3)
is an artist from the north of France. After playing for many years live in various nu-jazz & electronic bands in Lille & Paris, 
he started the downtempo project I√ãLO with many quality releases in all its sub genres. STR3E reflects his love for modern moody electronica.

Ariora
The greek artist Aiora has released on labels like PFL, Existence and Timewarp as well as on Ritchie Hawtins Minus Records after winning a remix competition for one of Hawtins songs.
Besides his musical career the Crete born music producer is running the stylish cocktail bar Kolokotroni 9 in Athens, hosting live Dj sets every other day. 
For his interpretation of Hiraeth he explores the darker vibes of his techno universe combined with african drum sounds.

Chris Zippel
aka CRSZPL is an electronic veteran music producer from Berlin who has worked with an impressive variety of well-known artists, including Pet Shop Boys, Klaus Schulze, Jose Padilla, Norah Jones, SNAP, Steve Lawler, Marmion, Namito and Vincent Littlehat.
His remix starts with a deephouse vibe, introducing later a reprogramming of a famous 90s acid bassline.

description:
Now on bandcamp:
http://genuinesounds.bandcamp.com/album/still-love-ep


Chris Zippel counts among the most prolific ambient/downtempo artists of the present time‚Ä¶ production work with Artists like the Pet Shop Boys, Robbie Williams, Ich und Ich, Snap and just lately Jose Padilla (with whom he just finished on top two remixes for the american Singer Norah Jones), speaks volumes.

His latest original single effort "Still Love", featuring the stand out voice of scandinavian songstress Sophie Tusnelda, creates a deep, unique vibe fuelled by the genuine Zippel trademark sound of course. "Sophie writes those kind of lyrics that come very close to my imagination of perfect melancholy" Chris says - and puts on smile.  

The silky original version of "Still Love" comes alongside three tantalizing remixes on this debut EP for Mole Listening Pearls.  
The Klangstein & Chris Zippel mix adds quite a vital dose of bass heavy downtempo groove to the sensual original - meanwhile, both the Aiora In Dub mix as well as the Chris Zippel & Dimitris Giakoumakis mix aim clearly at the adult dancefloors around the globe.
All that a tasty precursor to the upcoming Chris Zippel album... which incorporates an intense amount of inspiration that the vivid producer has soaked up in & around his new homebase, the white island of Ibiza, throughout the course of the last three years.

Just like on Chris¬¥s' previous Album, the refined cover artwork was created by Yoram Roth Photography.

title: Chris Zippel feat Sophie Tusnelda - Still Love  (4 Mixes Snippet/ Demo)

description:
JEN meets CHIN CHILLAZ - No Ordinary Life 
(soon out on stereo deluxe records)

With ‚ÄûNo Ordinary Life‚Äú, Washington based love poet JEN revisits her tantalizing 2008 debut album ‚ÄûMellow Dramas‚Äú once more... alongside infamous dubbernauts CHIN CHILLAZ (aka George Solar & Fe Wolter) that is. The dreamy, string-loaden original track gets the remix treatment in three deep updates this time around. 

First up is Ibiza based CHRIS ZIPPEL (aka GENUINE SOUNDS), a household name not only in the electronic and ambient world but also because of his sensual production work for a.o. THE PET SHOP BOYS, ROBBIE WILLIAMS and german mega pop act ICH & ICH. The GENUINE SOUNDS remix of ‚ÄûNo Ordinary Life‚Äú teleports the slow motion original straight onto the adult dub disco dancefloor with a wide smile... balearic for real!

Cologne based producer duo RUBBASOL, on the downtempo scene since the mid nineties and as of late active with providing trademark sound remixes for a.o. MASSIVAN and Budapest lounge dons GELKA (courtesy of the NIGHTMARES ON WAX imprint WAX ON Reords), provide a pretty hypnotic headnodder fueled by an analog synth pattern frenzy... and the inevitable echo chamber of course.   

Meanwhile, Auckland/New Zealand based dj/sound activist MORNING STEPPA has prepared an intriguingly positive post-dubstep chassis for JEN‚Äôs one-in-a-million voice and poetry to travel in safely.... even in southern hemispheres. 

In an ordinary world, this is definitely no ordinary remix package!
